name: Tesla Model Y
summary: Tesla has implemented price reductions in the United States for three of its electric vehicle models, namely the Model Y, Model X, and Model S, with each experiencing a $2,000 decrease. While Tesla's price reductions only apply to the US, their electric vehicles face competition from the Fisker Ocean SUV, which aims to rival Tesla's dominance. Furthermore, Tesla has discontinued its referral program and a rival electric vehicle manufacturer, NIO, has rolled out a battery swap station, sparking interest from a Tesla Model Y Juniper competitor.

summary: Legendary Yankees radio voice John Sterling has announced his retirement after 36 seasons and 5,631 games. Sterling, who is known for his enthusiastic catchphrases such as "it is high, it is far, it is gone," has been a beloved figure among Yankees fans for decades. He has been honored by the Yankees for his contributions to the team, and his retirement has been met with sadness by many. Sterling has expressed his gratitude for the opportunity to broadcast Yankees games and has said that he leaves "very, very happy."
